																if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) <= chess[tmpSite].charAt(3)){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) > chess[tmpSite].charAt(3))
																	recBt = null;
															}
														}
													}else if(chess[tmpSite] == null){
														chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
														chess[recSite] = null;
														bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
														bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
														recBt = null;
													}
												}
											}else if(siteChess.equals("r")){
												if(tmpSite == recSite-1 || tmpSite == recSite+8 || tmpSite == recSite-8){
													if(chess[tmpSite] != null){
														if(chess[recSite].charAt(0) != chess[tmpSite].charAt(0)){
															if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '1' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '6' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '6'){
																
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '1'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) != '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else {
																if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) <= chess[tmpSite].charAt(3)){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) > chess[tmpSite].charAt(3))
																	recBt = null;
															}
														}
													}else if(chess[tmpSite] == null){
														chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
														chess[recSite] = null;
														bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
														bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
														recBt = null;
													}
												}
											}else if(siteChess.equals("b")){
												if(tmpSite == recSite+1 || tmpSite == recSite-1 || tmpSite == recSite-8){
													if(chess[tmpSite] != null){
														if(chess[recSite].charAt(0) != chess[tmpSite].charAt(0)){
															if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '1' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '6' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '6'){
																
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '1'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) != '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else {
																if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) <= chess[tmpSite].charAt(3)){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) > chess[tmpSite].charAt(3))
																	recBt = null;
															}
														}
													}else if(chess[tmpSite] == null){
														chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
														chess[recSite] = null;
														bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
														bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
														recBt = null;
													}
												}
											}else if(siteChess.equals("m")){
												if(tmpSite == recSite+1 || tmpSite == recSite-1 || tmpSite == recSite+8 || tmpSite == recSite-8){
													if(chess[tmpSite] != null){
														if(chess[recSite].charAt(0) != chess[tmpSite].charAt(0)){
															if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '1' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '6' || chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) == '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '6'){
																
															}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) == '1'){
																if(chess[tmpSite].charAt(3) != '7'){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}
															}else {
																if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) <= chess[tmpSite].charAt(3)){
																	chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
																	chess[recSite] = null;
																	bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
																	bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
																	recBt = null;
																}else if(chess[recSite].charAt(3) > chess[tmpSite].charAt(3))
																	recBt = null;
															}
														}
													}else if(chess[tmpSite] == null){
														chess[tmpSite] = chess[recSite];
														chess[recSite] = null;
														bt[tmpSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[tmpSite] + ".png"));
														bt[recSite].setIcon(new ImageIcon(chess[recSite] + ".png"));
														recBt = null;
													}
												}
											}												
												
											
										}
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}catch(Exception ex){
						//e.printStackTrace();
					}
				}
			});
			jp.add(bt[i]);
		}
		this.add(jp);
	}
}
